id: pm-7zs0
title: Verify daily auto-release published to npm (release-health check)
description: "Recurring release-health verification. The date-based daily auto-release has silently failed before (padded-month changelog match skip; publish/Sentry-gate step failing post-tag). After any merge to main, confirm the next daily release both tagged a new vYYYY.M.D AND advanced npm 'latest'."
type: Reminder
status: in_progress
priority: 2
tags[3]: "area:release",living-map,reliability
created_at: "2026-06-07T10:24:45.889Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-29T07:22:36.765Z"
reminders[1]{at,text}:
  "2026-06-08T10:24:45.889Z",Confirm daily auto-release tagged a new version AND npm latest advanced; else inspect publish + Sentry-gate steps
assignee: claude-code-agent
author: maintainer-agent
parent: pm-u9d0
comments[24]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-10T14:44:30.277Z",maintainer-agent,"2026-06-10 daily auto-release (scheduled run 27258655654, 06:50Z) FAILED at sentry-telemetry-gate: PM-CLI-1J 'CommandError: {' — a CommandError whose message was the raw guided-error JSON envelope (code tracker_not_initialized) thrown by an ephemeral temp-dir script (readPmItemsForUpsert, source no longer on disk; 2 events 2026-06-09T21:34Z). Gate classifier fix already landed in PR #197 (fba75fb0, merged 11:34Z, adds 'tracker_not_initialized' to KNOWN_EXPECTED_HANDLED_CLI_ISSUE_PATTERNS) but AFTER the scheduled run. Recovery: resolved PM-CLI-1J in Sentry + re-dispatched auto-release.yml with push=true (run 27284359777). Will verify v2026.6.10 npm publish before closing."
  "2026-06-16T11:26:49.976Z",codex-sdk-cli-consolidation-20260616,"Auto-release gate reproduced locally with SENTRY_PERSONAL_ADMIN_TOKEN; failing high issue was PM-CLI-1Q (handled CommandError: all items failed to apply). Added count-agnostic handled pattern 'item(s) failed to apply' and blocking_short_ids/blocking_titles output for diagnostics. Gate now passes in strict mode with max-high=0."
  "2026-06-16T11:46:33.866Z",codex-sdk-cli-consolidation-20260616,"Release-health verification: sentry-telemetry gate now passes in strict mode (max-critical=0,max-high=0) after expected handled-CommandError classification update; output now includes blocking_short_ids/blocking_titles for actionable diagnostics."
  "2026-06-17T17:21:01.407Z",claude-code-agent,"2026-06-17 verification: after merging PR #263 (GH-216/217), dispatched auto-release with push=true → Release workflow succeeded → tag v2026.6.17 cut → npm @unbrained/pm-cli@2026.6.17 published. Telemetry stack healthy (12,982 events/24h, queue drained, all containers up); Sentry live with 0 new unresolved errors/24h. NOTE: the 02:35 UTC SCHEDULED auto-release still fails on the stale Sentry reliability gate (tracked separately as pm-nb08); manual dispatch is the current reliable path."
  "2026-06-18T23:13:15.492Z",claude-code-agent,"Release-health verification 2026-06-19 (post PR#290 merge): (1) Last published = npm 2026.6.17 == git v2026.6.17 (aligned). (2) The 2026-06-18 07:17Z scheduled Auto Release FAILED on a git push non-fast-forward — but that run executed BEFORE the push-retry fix bf35af26 merged at 16:19 CEST, so it ran old code. The fetch+rebase+retry now lives in scripts/release/run-release-pipeline.mjs pushReleaseRefs. (3) Manually dispatched Auto Release dry-run on current main (run 27794655651): FULLY GREEN — build, docs/static/coverage gates, tests, version compute, changelog, and the Sentry reliability gate all pass. (4) Telemetry stack healthy: all containers up, API ok (v2026.6.17), RabbitMQ queue drained (0 ready), 15061 Postgres events/24h (real-time). (5) Sentry: queryable with admin token; newest unresolved issue 2026-06-13, all expected CommandErrors, NO new errors from PR#290. Conclusion: the next scheduled cron (35 2 * * * UTC) will publish 2026.6.18/.19 automatically with the fixed push path. Verify npm picks it up after the next run."
  "2026-06-19T05:58:34.548Z",claude-code-agent,"2026-06-19 release-health check (post PR#297 merge): main CI green at 4c32fe56; Sentry gate critical=0/high=0; telemetry real-time (14785 events/24h, queue backlog 0); auto-release push-race fixed (pm-5oti/bf35af26). Pending: no npm publish since v2026.6.17 — next daily schedule (07:17 UTC) is first run with the push-race fix and should cut v2026.6.19."
  "2026-06-19T06:18:21.291Z",claude-code-agent,"RESOLVED 2026-06-19: v2026.6.19 published to npm. Manual Auto Release dispatch (push=true) SUCCEEDED end-to-end — the push-race fix (pm-5oti/bf35af26) held (tag v2026.6.19 pushed, Release workflow green, verify-published-release passed). First successful release since v2026.6.17; ships 21+ commits incl PR#297 (list csv/table + context --fields). Daily auto-release confirmed working."
  "2026-06-25T17:43:08.790Z",codex-gpt5,"Audit evidence 2026-06-25: npm latest @unbrained/pm-cli is 2026.6.24; local package version is 2026.6.24; Auto Release run 28183051760 completed successfully at 2026-06-25T16:03:31Z. Item remains claimed by codex-sdk-cli-consolidation-20260616, so no closure/ownership change made by this agent."
  "2026-06-26T07:24:47.324Z",codex-sdk-cli-continue,"Release-health evidence 2026-06-26: npm latest remains @unbrained/pm-cli 2026.6.24 and latest tag is v2026.6.24. Scheduled Auto Release run 28221678293 failed before publishing because RELEASE_PAT is absent from the release environment; open GitHub issue #374 tracks the current blocked daily release. Manual workflow_dispatch run 28219218329 was push=false dry_run=true and therefore only confirms gates, not publish."
  "2026-06-26T07:29:59.238Z",codex-sdk-cli-continue,"Evidence: release-health branch verification completed. The active external blocker remains RELEASE_PAT absence in the release environment; the branch improves future scheduled failure issues so agents can read detected preflight state directly. npm latest/tag remain 2026.6.24/v2026.6.24 until maintainer configures RELEASE_PAT and reruns Auto Release with push=true."
  "2026-06-26T21:06:16.131Z",codex-gpt5,"Release-health evidence 2026-06-26 continuation: GitHub issue #374 is still open for scheduled Auto Release blocked before publish because RELEASE_PAT_CONFIGURED=false in the release environment. Latest inspected Auto Release schedule run 28221678293 failed before the release pipeline; workflow_dispatch run 28219218329 was push=false/dry_run=true and only proved gates. Current code-side checks are healthy: Sentry/telemetry gate ok (critical=0 high=0, telemetry finish_error_rate_pct=0.7), pm-changelog latest and installed version are 2026.6.20, package doctor deep ok. No release-health code patch is included in the CodeFactor branch; maintainer must configure RELEASE_PAT/RELEASE_PUSH_TOKEN and rerun Auto Release with push=true before this reminder can close."
  "2026-06-26T23:23:45.393Z",codex-sdk-cli-continuation,"Release-health evidence: Sentry dependency refresh task pm-4dz7 verified release/telemetry gates after updating @sentry/node 10.62.0 and @sentry/cli 3.6.0. Auto Release remains blocked by external RELEASE_PAT absence in the release environment; latest scheduled Auto Release run 28221678293 failed before publish and issue #374 remains open. Code-side release/telemetry gates are healthy: live Sentry critical/high = 0, telemetry finish_error_rate_pct = 0.73, pm-changelog 2026.6.20 check unchanged, package doctor deep ok."
  "2026-06-27T07:02:03.202Z",codex-sdk-cli-20260627,"Implementation note: pnpm changelog:pm:check installed pm-changelog 2026.6.27 from npm, activated project changelog commands, and left CHANGELOG.md unchanged. Reusing release-health item pm-7zs0 for the package refresh; issue #374 remains externally blocked on missing RELEASE_PAT."
  "2026-06-27T07:06:13.278Z",codex-sdk-cli-20260627,"Verification note: pnpm changelog:pm:check passes in the real repo with pm-changelog 2026.6.27 and CHANGELOG.md unchanged. Not linked as a pm test because changelog generation is a real-repo package-owned verification path, not a schema/tracker sandbox test."
  "2026-06-27T07:09:59.358Z",codex-sdk-cli-20260627,"Evidence: refreshed project pm-changelog package to npm version 2026.6.27 and verified node dist/cli.js package doctor --project --detail deep --json. Linked tests passed: pm test pm-7zs0 --run --progress (3/3). Real-repo pnpm changelog:pm:check passed with CHANGELOG.md unchanged. Auto Release issue #374 remains externally blocked by missing RELEASE_PAT in the release environment; code-side diagnostics already fail fast and report the exact missing secret."
  "2026-06-27T07:21:25.279Z",codex-sdk-cli-20260627,"Final evidence: release-health/package checks after pm-changelog 2026.6.27 refresh remain clean. Verified pnpm changelog:pm:check unchanged, package doctor deep ok, pm health summary ok, Sentry/telemetry gate ok with critical=0 high=0 and telemetry finish_error_rate_pct=0.72. Current external blocker remains GitHub issue #374: scheduled Auto Release run 28280770086 fails because RELEASE_PAT is absent from the release environment."
  "2026-06-27T07:41:34.851Z",codex-sdk-cli-20260627,"Release-health evidence for PR #385: managed project package refresh remains on pm-changelog 2026.6.27; pnpm changelog:pm:check regenerated in check mode and reported CHANGELOG.md unchanged with item_count=1357 and bytes=218600. Package doctor deep reports pm-changelog active with command paths changelog export/generate and no warnings. Auto Release issue #374 remains externally blocked by missing RELEASE_PAT in the release environment, confirmed from GitHub scheduled run evidence before this implementation. Sentry/telemetry gate passed after review fixes with critical=0 high=0, access_ok=true, telemetry finish_error_rate_pct=0.72, failures_without_error_code_rows=0."
  "2026-06-27T08:04:27.572Z",codex-sdk-cli-20260627,"Merge evidence: PR #385 merged to main as 753410df with pm-changelog project package refreshed to 2026.6.27 and package doctor deep clean. Post-merge release-health checks passed: pm health summary ok, history drift validation ok, package doctor deep ok, and Sentry/telemetry gate critical=0 high=0 telemetry finish_error_rate_pct=0.72. Daily Auto Release remains externally blocked by GitHub issue #374 because RELEASE_PAT is absent from the release environment; no code-side blocker found in this lane."
  "2026-06-27T23:24:23.273Z",claude-code-agent,"Implementation start: duplicate-safe all-status search found existing release-health item pm-7zs0 plus blocked external credential issue pm-9gxi/#374; no new pm item created. Scope is code-side auto-release issue lifecycle cleanup: close the blocked scheduled-release issue only after a scheduled run actually publishes a tag and the downstream Release workflow succeeds, while preserving the external RELEASE_PAT blocker."
  "2026-06-27T23:32:57.898Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: implemented scheduled Auto Release success cleanup so a scheduled run only closes the stale Auto Release blocked issue after it publishes a tag and the downstream Release workflow succeeds. Validation passed: focused workflow contract test, linked pm test run 7/7, pnpm build, pnpm typecheck, pnpm lint, pnpm quality:static, pnpm contracts:check, pnpm security:scan, pnpm audit --audit-level moderate, pnpm changelog:pm:check using pm-changelog 2026.6.27 with CHANGELOG.md unchanged, pm health summary ok, history drift ok, full coverage 100/100/100/100, Sentry/telemetry gate critical=0 high=0 telemetry finish_error_rate_pct=0.76, and isolated temp-directory smoke passed with PM_PATH/PM_GLOBAL_PATH at /tmp/tmp.zLjtqymDaG. pm validate still reports existing resolution metadata backlog of 258 closed items; not introduced by this branch."
  "2026-06-27T23:42:55.639Z",claude-code-agent,"Review fix evidence: addressed CodeRabbit/Cubic feedback on PR #392. Auto Release now exports the tagged release commit SHA with published_sha and uses it in the success cleanup comment; stale blocked-issue query/close failures now log and exit 0 so a successful scheduled publish cannot trigger the blocked-release alert. Post-fix validation passed: focused workflow contract test, pnpm build, pnpm quality:static, git diff --check, and pm test pm-7zs0 --run --progress 7/7."
  "2026-06-27T23:51:57.067Z",claude-code-agent,"Final review fix evidence: addressed unresolved Gemini thread on PR #392 by changing the scheduled-success cleanup guard from an empty-string comparison to a direct published_tag truthiness check, preventing skipped/no-publish runs with absent outputs from entering stale-issue cleanup. Validation passed: focused workflow contract test, pnpm build, git diff --check, and pm test pm-7zs0 --run --progress 7/7."
  "2026-06-28T12:06:18.990Z",claude-code-agent,"Release-health update: latest scheduled Auto Release run 28314163942 on 2026-06-28 failed at the configured preflight before publishing because RELEASE_PAT_CONFIGURED=false while INPUT_PUSH=true and INPUT_DRY_RUN=false. The log explicitly says RELEASE_PAT is required before Auto Release can push the checked version commit/tag to protected main; SENTRY_PERSONAL_ADMIN_TOKEN_CONFIGURED=true in the same run. Manual workflow_dispatch Auto Release runs on 2026-06-25 and 2026-06-26 succeeded, so this remains an external release-environment secret/permission blocker tracked by GitHub issue #374, not a code regression in this branch."
  "2026-06-29T07:22:36.765Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: refreshed actions/cache pin to 6.1.0 across CI, Auto Release, Release, and Nightly workflows from GitHub Dependabot PR #398. Workflow contract tests passed, pnpm build passed, package doctor deep ok, changelog generated by pm-changelog 2026.6.27 and check unchanged. Current Auto Release issue #374 remains externally blocked by missing RELEASE_PAT in the release environment; code-side release and telemetry gates are healthy with Sentry critical=0/high=0 and telemetry finish_error_rate_pct=0.74."
